text: Maureen Tuimalealiifano (born 17 October 1970) is a Samoan archer. Tuimalealiifano competed at the 2012 Summer Olympics.Maureen TuimalealiifanoMaureen TUIMALEALIIFANO == References == Category:Archers Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Olympians for Samoa
